sentences.english: Caesar, William the Conquerer allopted for a full invasion of England.
sentences.chinese: 凱撒，威廉這樣的征服者都選擇完全的侵略英格蘭。

sentences.english: New England had frosts in July.
sentences.chinese: 七月的新英格蘭地區還在霜凍。

sentences.english: Do you know what the New Englanders thought of this?
sentences.chinese: 您知道新英格蘭居民對此案的看法嗎？

sentences.english: Shall weave old England's winding sheet .
sentences.chinese: 爲老英格蘭織起裹屍布。

sentences.english: A town on the northern coast of the Isle of Wight off southern England.
sentences.chinese: 英格蘭南部威特島北岸的一個城鎮。

sentences.english: England or Great Britain. Often used poetically.
sentences.chinese: 阿爾比恩英格蘭或大不列顛。

sentences.english: It arranged for its importation into England with the intention of re-exporting it.
sentences.chinese: 被告意圖將這批藥品進口至英格蘭後再轉出口。

sentences.english: Manchester United have won the top division title in England no less than 19 times.
sentences.chinese: 曼聯在以往的英格蘭頂級聯賽中至少成功奪魁19次。

sentences.english: The Royals have taken Chelsea's England Under-21 left-back Bertrand on loan.
sentences.chinese: 切爾西的英格蘭U21國腳伯特蘭將通過租借加盟。

sentences.english: England still hasn't caught up to the concept of the hyphenated identity.
sentences.chinese: 英格蘭還不能跟上聯衆認同的觀念。

sentences.english: After the large and treacherous wind storm that hit New England a few weeks ago, I lost power.
sentences.chinese: 我家在險惡的強風暴襲擊新英格蘭後幾周停電。

sentences.english: The Spanish Armada sailed to England in1588.
sentences.chinese: 西班牙無敵艦隊在一五八八年派遣到英格蘭。

sentences.english: In England, the best plums are grown in Kent and the Vale of Evesham.
sentences.chinese: 在英格蘭，最上乘的李子種植在肯特和伊弗珊谷。

sentences.english: So let a more traditional type of manager come in.
sentences.chinese: 僱個更英格蘭的教練吧。

sentences.english: Why did the Emperor Hadrian build a wall right across England?
sentences.chinese: 爲什麼哈德良皇帝建造了一座橫跨英格蘭的城牆？
